The paper deals with load balancing in distributed systems, which is a topic that falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The use of mean field fluid limit methods suggests that the paper may also fall under the category of Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) or Systems and Control (cs.SY). The paper also involves analyzing algorithms, which could place it under the category of Performance (cs.PF) or Mathematical Analysis (cs.MA).
